DEPARTMENT; LOS ANGELES TO LONG BEACH LIGHT RAIL LINE; EMBEZZLEMENT; CONTRACTS; 
CONSULTANTS; DISMISSALS; STACY, JOHN R; BUILDING INDUSTRY -- SECURITY 
</P>
