AIRPORT; MINORITY OWNED BUSINESS; JOINT VENTURES; LOS ANGELES -- FINANCES; LOS 
ANGELES DEPARTMENT OF AIRPORTS; HOST INTERNATIONAL INC; FAVORITISM; BROOKINS, H 
H; DIXON, BETTY; DIXON, JULIAN C 
</P>
