-- EASTERN EUROPE; SUMMIT CONFERENCES; GOVERNMENT REFORM; EASTERN EUROPE -- 
GOVERNMENT; MILITARY FORCE REDUCTIONS; BUSH, GEORGE; GORBACHEV, MIKHAIL S 
</P>
