<P>
FOOTBALL PLAYERS; COLLEGE ATHLETICS; UNIVERSITY OF SOUTHERN CALIFORNIA; 
UNIVERSITY OF CALIFORNIA LOS ANGELES; MARINOVICH, TODD; JOHNSON, BRET 
</P>
